---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'SafetyWing in UAE', level: 2 },
  { id: 'compliance', text: 'DHA/HAAD Compliance', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Choose SafetyWing', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in UAE', href: '/countries/uae/insurance' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing Review', href: '/providers/safetywing' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing vs Cigna', href: '/compare/safetywing-vs-cigna-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'price', header: 'Price' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Nomad Insurance', coverage: 'Travel medical', price: '$45-55/mo' },
  { plan: 'Remote Health', coverage: 'Health insurance', price: '$150-200/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="SafetyWing in UAE"
  description="Guide to using SafetyWing in UAE. Budget nomad coverage and whether it meets UAE visa requirements."
  headline="SafetyWing in UAE"
  subheadline="Budget travel medical insurance for digital nomads—but is it right for UAE?"
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/uae-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get a SafetyWing Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/safetywing"
>
  <h2 id="overview">SafetyWing in UAE</h2>
  <p>
    SafetyWing is popular among digital nomads for its affordable travel medical insurance. However, for UAE residents, SafetyWing has significant limitations that make it unsuitable as primary coverage.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <p class="text-amber-800 text-sm">
      <strong>Important:</strong> SafetyWing Nomad Insurance is travel medical insurance, not comprehensive health insurance. It likely does NOT meet UAE visa requirements.
    </p>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Need UAE-Compliant Coverage?"
    description="Consider proper health insurance for UAE visa requirements."
    buttonText="See Compliant Plans"
    buttonHref="/go/safetywing"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="compliance">DHA/HAAD Compliance</h2>
  <p>
    SafetyWing's Nomad Insurance is unlikely to meet DHA or HAAD requirements:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>It's travel medical insurance, not health insurance</li>
    <li>Coverage limits ($250K) may not meet UAE requirements</li>
    <li>No outpatient coverage (required for DHA compliance)</li>
    <li>Pre-existing conditions not covered</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    SafetyWing's Remote Health product is actual health insurance and may be more suitable, but you should verify compliance directly.
  </p>

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Nomad Insurance vs Remote Health</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Nomad Insurance:</strong> Travel medical only. Emergency and acute care. NOT suitable for UAE residency.</li>
    <li><strong>Remote Health:</strong> Actual health insurance. May meet requirements but verify compliance.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Choose SafetyWing in UAE</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Potentially Suitable</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>Short-term visitors (not residents)</li>
        <li>Digital nomads passing through</li>
        <li>Those with other primary coverage</li>
        <li>Remote Health users (verify compliance)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-900 mb-3">Not Suitable</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-red-800">
        <li>UAE residents needing visa-compliant insurance</li>
        <li>Those needing comprehensive coverage</li>
        <li>Anyone with pre-existing conditions</li>
        <li>Families requiring maternity coverage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    For UAE residents, we recommend proper international health insurance that meets DHA/HAAD requirements. See our <a href="/countries/uae/insurance">UAE insurance guide</a> for compliant options.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Need Proper UAE Coverage?"
    description="Compare DHA-compliant international health insurance plans."
    buttonText="See Compliant Plans"
    buttonHref="/go/safetywing"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> SafetyWing Nomad Insurance is likely NOT suitable for UAE visa requirements. Always verify compliance before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
